The paper discusses the future of machine programming, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The three pillars of research mentioned in the paper - intention, invention, and adaptation - are all related to programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the focus on autonomous evolution of software suggests a connection to systems and control (cs.SY).
